68px;text-indent: 24px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;font-size: 15px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: 宋体\">3、处理办法：点我的电脑右键管理》本地用户和组》用户，查看</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif\">SERVU</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: 宋体\">账户是否存在，如果存在请直接修改一个密码记住备后面使用；如果没有就新建立一个。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 744px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;line-height: 24px;width: 768px;text-indent: 24px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;font-size: 15px\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20150814/1439519134520211.jpg\" style=\";padding: 0px;border: none;width: 744px\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 744px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;line-height: 24px;width: 768px;text-indent: 24px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;font-size: 15px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: 宋体\">4、到服务管理找到</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif\">SERVU</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;width: 768px;font-family: 宋体\">服务》右键属性》选择登录即可正常启动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 744px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;line-height: 24px;width: 768px;text-indent: 24px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;font-size: 15px\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" src=\"/ueditor/php/uploa