x; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">域名注册产品页面搜索如下图：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/73921402468114510.png\" width=\"782\" height=\"492\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 782px; height: 492px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">三.&nbsp;输入要查询的域名类型及域名，勾选相应的后缀名，点击搜索即可反馈查询结果，显示该域名有无被注册及各注册商的价格<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/73421402468135507.png\" width=\"334\" height=\"224\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 334px; height: 224px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/46101402468175699.png\" width=\"793\" height=\"479\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 793px; height: 479px;\"/><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/94681402468209421.png\" width=\"752\" height=\"431\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 752px; height: 431px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">四.&nbsp;根据反馈的查询结果选择需要购买的域名及注册商，点击立即注册，进入域名注册详情信息页面<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/1901402468242473.png\" width=\"755\" height=\"264\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 755px; height: 264px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/19271402468355213.png\" width=\"714\" height=\"345\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 714px; height: 345px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/691402468411718.png\" width=\"552\" height=\"423\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 552px; height: 423px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">详情页面请先确认域名注册的基本信息，查看是否有代金券可使用，账户是否有足够的余额可购买域名。如果余额不足，可点击“点击充值”按钮，进行在线支付<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/39981402468453965.png\" width=\"765\" height=\"348\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 765px; height: 348px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/43461402468600761.jpg\" width=\"617\" height=\"189\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 617px; height: 189px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">域名详情信息确认完毕后，请按照要求填写域名所有人信息，信息务必确保真实。填完信息后点击立即注册即可成功注册该域名。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/20451402468636562.png\" width=\"836\" height=\"621\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 836px; height: 621px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">注：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>如果您注册的域名为.cn/.公司/.网络/.中国&nbsp;后缀域名，请您注册成功之后上传资料进行审核，经CNNIC审核通过后方能正常解析使，否则域名将会被锁定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">企业注册需提交：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>a、有效的企业营业执照或组织机构代码证扫描件；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>b、注册联系人的身份证明扫描件；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>个人注册需提交：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>有效的域名持有人身份证扫描件。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>注册商不同，资料上传方式不同，请按照以下方式进行资料上传：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>a、中国数据：注册之后请登录&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://dns.4cun.com/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; outline: none;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;\">http://dns.4cun.com/</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;进行资料上传;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>b、万网：注册之后请联系商务人员进行资料上传。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>c、新网互联：注册之后请登录&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://mgt.dns.com.cn/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; outline: none;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体;\">http://mgt.dns.com.cn/</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;进行资料上传。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>五．域名注册成功后，跳转到会员中心-我的订单信息中显示域名注册成功后的详情页面。即可管理自己的域名。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/57761402468683297.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"238\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 750px; height: 238px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><img title=\"如何申请域名\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zzidc.com/upload/image/20140611/18301402469595994.jpg\" width=\"702\" height=\"523\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; width: 702px; height: 523px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 744px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, arial, sans-serif, Helvetica, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">注：.cn/.公司/.网络/.中国&nbsp;后缀域名需要点击“域名实名验证系统”提交资料到认证。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; width: 768px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '2015-07-02 09:50:05', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
